            <title>[DERBY-5620] Replace illegal characters from test name when creating the failure folder</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-5620</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Since the name of a JUnit test case can be any string, it should be sanitized and bad characters should be replaced with a valid one.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
